)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/upload\"><code>upload</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/withCredentials\"><code>withCredentials</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Métodos</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/abort\"><code>abort()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/getAllResponseHeaders\"><code>getAllResponseHeaders()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/getResponseHeader\"><code>getResponseHeader()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/msCachingEnabled\"><code>msCachingEnabled()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><em><code>open()</code></em></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/overrideMimeType\"><code>overrideMimeType()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/send\"><code>send()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/setRequestHeader\"><code>setRequestHeader()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Eventos</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/abort_event\"><code>abort</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/error_event\"><code>error</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/load_event\"><code>load</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/loadend_event\"><code>loadend</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/loadstart_event\"><code>loadstart</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/progress_event\"><code>progress</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/readystatechange_event\"><code>readystatechange</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/timeout_event\"><code>timeout</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Herança:</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequestEventTarget\"><code>XMLHttpRequestEventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Páginas relacionadas a XMLHttpRequest</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/FormData\"><code>FormData</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/ProgressEvent\"><code>ProgressEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequestEventTarget\"><code>XMLHttpRequestEventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"A documentação sobre isto ainda não foi escrita; por favor considere contribuir!\"><code>XMLHttpRequestUpload</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>O&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest\"><code>XMLHttpRequest</code></a> método<code><strong>open()</strong></code> inicializa uma nova requisição, ou reinicializa uma requisição já existente.</p>\n\n<div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect2\"><strong>Note:</strong> Chamar este método para uma requisição já ativada&nbsp; (uma que&nbsp;<code>open()</code>&nbsp;já tenha sido chamada) é equivalente a chamar <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/abort\" title=\"abort()\"><code>abort()</code></a>.</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sintaxe","title":"Sintaxe","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><em>XMLHttpRequest</em>.open(<var>method</var>,<var> url</var>)\n<em>XMLHttpRequest</em>.open(<var>method</var>,<var> url</var>,<var> async)</var>\n<em>XMLHttpRequest</em>.open(<var>method</var>,<var> url</var>,<var> async</var>,<var> user</var>)\n<em>XMLHttpRequest</em>.open(<var>method</var>,<var> url</var>,<var> async</var>,<var> user</var>,<var> password</var>)\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parâmetros","title":"Parâmetros","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"method\"><code>method</code></dt>\n <dd>O <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/HTTP/Methods\">método de requisição HTTP</a>&nbsp;para ser usado, como&nbsp;<code>\"GET\"</code>, <code>\"POST\"</code>, <code>\"PUT\"</code>, <code>\"DELETE\"</code>, etc. Ignorado para URLs não-HTTP(S).</dd>\n <dt id=\"url\"><code>url</code></dt>\n <dd>Um <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>DOMString</code></a> representando a URL para enviar a requisição.</dd>\n <dt id=\"async\"><code>async</code> <span class=\"badge inline optional\">Optional</span></dt>\n <dd>Parâmetro booleano opcional, valor padrão&nbsp;<code>true</code>, indica quando realizar a operação&nbsp;de forma assíncrona. Se este valor for&nbsp;<code>false</code>, o método&nbsp;<code>send()</code>&nbsp;não retorna&nbsp;nada até que a resposta da requisição seja recebida.&nbsp;Se o valor for&nbsp;<code>true</code>, notificação de uma transação concluída é provida usando&nbsp;event listeners. Isso&nbsp;<em>deve</em>&nbsp;ser verdadeiro se o atributo&nbsp;<code>multipart</code> é <code>true</code>, ou uma exceção será lançada.\n <div class=\"note notecard\" id=\"sect3\"><strong>Nota:</strong>&nbsp;Requisições Síncronas no thread principal podem ser facilmente disruptivas para a experiência de usuário e devem ser evitadas; de fato, muitos navegadores descontinuaram inteiramente o suporte para XHR síncrono no thread principal.&nbsp;Requisições síncronas são permitidas nos&nbsp;<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Worker\"><code>Worker</code></a>s.</div>\n </dd>\n <dt id=\"user\"><code>user</code> <span class=\"badge inline optional\">Optional</span></dt>\n <dd>O nome de usuário opcional para ser usado em autenticação; por padrão, isso é o valor&nbsp;<code>null</code>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"password\"><code>password</code> <span class=\"badge inline optional\">Optional</span></dt>\n <dd>A senha de usuário opcional para ser usado em autenticação; por padrão, isso é o valor&nbsp;<code>null</code>.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificações","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Especificação</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comentário</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://xhr.spec.whatwg.org/#the-open()-method\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">XMLHttpRequest<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'open()' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Padrão em tempo real</span></td>\n   <td>\n    <p>Padrão WHATWG</p>\n   </td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.XMLHttpRequest.open","dataURL":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/open/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"veja_também","title":"Veja também","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/Using_XMLHttpRequest\">Usando XMLHttpRequest</a></li>\n <li>Métodos Relacionados ao <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest\"><code>XMLHttpRequest</code></a>: <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/setRequestHeader\" title=\"setRequestHeader()\"><code>setRequestHeader()</code></a>,<a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/send\" title=\"send()\"><code>send()</code></a>, e <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/abort\" title=\"abort()\"><code>abort()</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Sintaxe","id":"sintaxe"},{"text":"Especificações","id":"especificações"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Veja também","id":"veja_também"}],"summary":"O XMLHttpRequest métodoopen() inicializa uma nova requisição, ou reinicializa uma requisição já existente.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"XMLHttpRequest.open()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"XMLHttpRequest.open()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"XMLHttpRequest.open()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"XMLHttpRequest.open()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"XMLHttpRequest.open()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/api/xmlhttprequest/open","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/api/xmlhttprequest/open/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API","title":"APIs da Web"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest","title":"XMLHttpRequest"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/XMLHttpRequest/open","title":"XMLHttpRequest.open()"}],"pageTitle":"XMLHttpRequest.open() - APIs da Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}